            "stanza_text": "Dans la forêt mouillée et verte,\nComme deux rudes compagnons,\nNous allions à la découverte\nCueillir au loin des champignons."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Nous n’y connaissions pas grand’chose;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Comme des enfants, tous les deux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Nous goûtions leur chair blanche et rose;",
